wiki.content: The song is featured on Madonna's latest album, MDNA, which was released in 2012. A remixed version of the song was performed by Kitty Brucknell on her Glamour & Damage tour of China User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
wiki.summary: The song is featured on Madonna's latest album, MDNA, which was released in 2012. A remixed version of the song was performed by Kitty Brucknell on her Glamour & Damage tour of China
